casebody.head_matter:
Raymond P. VINNIE, petitioner,
v.
Bruce R. HENRY, et al.
No. 18-6221.
Supreme Court of the United States
Dec. 10, 2018.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari to the Appeals Court of Massachusetts dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
